| Adi | Knowledge sharing (teaching) | HIGH | HIGH | STABLE |
| Brandon (1:1) | Value (strategic framing, not just updates) | MEDIUM | MEDIUM-HIGH | IMPROVING — 3/24 annual review: Richard connected artifact shipping to communication style. Genuine vulnerability. |
| Brandon (group) | Presence + Value (be heard, say something strategic) | LOW | LOW | STUCK — 3/24 weekly sync: Richard quiet during Andrew/Stacey segments. Contributed on testing/MX only. |
