## Integration with Other Organs

The nervous system reads FROM every organ but writes TO only a few:

| Reads From | What It Checks |
|-----------|---------------|
| Brain | Decision outcomes, principle application frequency |
| Eyes | Prediction accuracy, metric trends vs expectations |
| Hands | Task completion patterns, overdue recurrence |
| Memory | Relationship accuracy, meeting brief usefulness |
| Device | Delegation status, tool adoption, hook reliability |
| Heart | Loop run frequency, experiment success rate |
| rw-tracker.md | Mediocrity patterns, weekly scorecard |
| Soul | Identity alignment, preference drift |

| Writes To | What It Updates |
|----------|----------------|
| Brain | Decision OUTCOME fields, principle rank changes, Five Levels position |
| Device | Delegation status updates, failed delegation escalations |
| Heart | Experiment queue suggestions based on calibration gaps |
| rw-tracker.md | Pattern trajectory updates |
| changelog.md | Calibration report logs |

