## When to Read This File

- Friday weekly check-in — generate the calibration report
- Monthly deep review — full system health assessment
- When a decision's outcome window closes — run Loop 1
- When the trainer flags a pattern as STUCK — check Loop 3 for trajectory
- When a delegation due date passes — run Loop 4
- When the system feels bloated or slow — run Loop 5
- Quarterly — run Loop 6 (principle evolution)
- After Hedy sync — run Loop 7 (meeting communication scoring)
- Monthly or after structural changes — run Loop 8 (coherence audit)
